## Status
- **Completed:**
  - **TotalPricer brand** lock — every "Defy / DEFY / OpenPrice / DEFY CLOUD / Dare to Defy / Brokers Close Harder / Powered by DEFY TPO" string stripped from src/. Login + signup hero now reads "TQL BENCH". Mobile drawer header reads "TQL Pricer · Total Quality Lending". Desktop wordmark is "TotalPricer" (Pricer in TQL teal).
  - **Top nav layout (sidebar hidden)** — desktop sidebar (`hidden lg:flex` → `hidden`), `<main>` no longer has `lg:ml-[200px]`. Top header rebuilt with logo + 4 nav buttons (Chat Live Now, New Scenario, Flash Submit, User Admin) + auth cluster on far right behind a divider. Mobile drawer kept as-is.
  - **Print PDF** auto-downloads via `/api/rate-quote-pdf` (no print preview, no popup window). Server-side PDF built with pdf-lib — full /tql-brand: 90px teal header band + 3px Sky Signal stripe, 44pt hero rate/price, APR + P&I stats card, scenario block with alternating row tints, multi-page rate-stack table. fitText() truncates with ellipsis. Footer shows NMLS + page N of M.
  - **Rate stacks scoped to ONE program** across Print PDF, Email Client Quote, and Send Full Quote. New `collectProgramRateStack(programs, name)` replaces `collectFullRateStack` everywhere user-facing. Send Full Quote modal filters `allCandidates` by `selected.programName` before passing through.
  - **Reserve Rate email rebuilt** with `buildReserveRequestEmail()`. Same TQL design language as the other emails (teal header band + Sky Signal stripe, hero rate/price, APR + P&I, raw investor block, broker contact, scenario inputs alternating-row table, rate ladder for the program, NMLS footer). Goes FROM `TQL TotalPricer <TQLQuote@tqltpo.com>` TO `lockdesk@tqlend.com`. Subject `RATE RESERVATION — <rate>% @ <price> — <raw investor program>`. Lock Desk sees raw investor names; broker UI never does.
  - **FROM sender unified** as `TQLQuote@tqltpo.com` across `api/send-email.ts` (default), `api/flash-submit-request.ts`, and `handleRowReserve` override. Verified-domain guard on `tqltpo.com` / `tqlend.com`.
  - **Direct PDF download endpoint** — `api/rate-quote-pdf.ts` returns `application/pdf` with `Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="TQL-Quote-<program>-<rate>-<price>.pdf"`. Frontend hits it via fetch + Blob + hidden `<a download>` click.
  - **Pill-toggle blank-screen bug** killed for good — replaced every `<label><input sr-only></label>` with plain `<button type="button" aria-pressed={...}>`. Chrome no longer focus-scrolls into an absolute-positioned hidden input. Verified live with gstack: `documentElement.scrollTop` stays at 0 after every pill click.
  - **Chat with a Human** restored to both desktop top nav + mobile drawer (Supabase-backed live chat panel was already wired in the modal stack but unreachable).
  - **GEMINI_API_KEY** rotated in Vercel production (mirrors `.env.local`).
  - **Mobile polish** — quote modals use `text-base sm:text-sm` (>= 16px font on mobile to prevent iOS auto-zoom on focus), `inputMode="email"`, `autoCapitalize="none"`, `autoCorrect="off"`, `py-3` tap targets.
- **Next Up:** Validate live PDF + email rendering with a real DSCR scenario; gut-check the Lock Desk reservation email body.
- **Blockers:** None.

