## Key Decisions
- **One unified card UI for results** — same "EXPAND PRICING OPTIONS" card style for broker default (1 or 2 cards) and admin unlocked (every program with `Raw · Admin` chip). Hero / companion / stack-table cards from earlier iterations all removed.
- **Admin gate is a single passcode (`TQLFAITH`)** that flips `showRawInvestor` — toggles raw investor names AND skips the 99.000–101.750 price-band filter so admins see every product regardless of band.
- **Rate stack scope** is always the SELECTED program's own ladder. Multi-investor leakage was the #1 brand risk and is now eliminated everywhere user-facing.
- **Reserve email is the sole place RAW investor data ships** — and only because it goes to Lock Desk, never to the broker.
- **Print PDF is server-side** (pdf-lib via `/api/rate-quote-pdf`) — keeps the bundle slim and the layout pixel-precise; bypasses print preview.

