## Technical Notes
- **Pill toggles must NOT be `<label><input sr-only></label>`**. Chrome focus-scrolls absolute-positioned hidden inputs into view, which corrupts overflow:hidden body layout. Always use `<button type="button" aria-pressed={...}>`.
- **Email FROM domain whitelist** in `api/send-email.ts` — only `tqltpo.com` / `tqlend.com` pass the verified check; anything else falls back to default. Resend rejects unverified senders.
- **OB pricing pipeline** unchanged from earlier session: per-product detail fetch → `collectProgramRateStack` (broker) or full ladder (admin) → render as a single card with EXPAND PRICING OPTIONS. DSCR 5% PPP pinning + 3% PPP companion still in place.
- **Encompass field 305 / loan number retry** logic untouched (4× backoff via `/fieldReader` then `/fieldWriter`).
- **PDF generation**: pdf-lib only — letter-size 612x792, margin 44, multi-page support via ensureRoom() with continuation header. Fonts limited to Helvetica / HelveticaBold (built-in StandardFonts).
- **Mobile-friendly emails**: max-width 600px tables, system-font stack only (Manrope / Inter not safe across Outlook/Gmail), inline styles, viewport meta.

